    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >逃离 Timefront</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328840/extras/64e19fa51f755d3ebb0b68e9cd337942.poster.avif?t=1769610039\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328840/extras/64e19fa51f755d3ebb0b68e9cd337942.webm?t=1769610039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328840/extras/64e19fa51f755d3ebb0b68e9cd337942.mp4?t=1769610039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地图的区域会逐渐被封锁，你必须为剩余的资源和领地而战。你会选择坚守阵地战斗到最后，还是建立强大的军队与经济力量，将一切敌人摧毁殆尽？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 个完全不同的种族，拥有独特的单位、指挥官和建筑。[\\/p][\\/*]</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >流畅的战斗体验与智能的目标系统，操作响应迅速。[\\/p][\\/*]</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过 100 种被动技能与阵营加成，自由搭配，打造属于你的独特战斗风格。[\\/p][\\/*]</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地图会随时间逐渐缩小，封锁部分区域，带来紧张刺激的对局体验。[\\/p][\\/*][\\/list]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[\\/p]<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >史诗级战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328840/extras/b24f2f48ff8dd32c72b6bc63f0fdc0bd.poster.avif?t=1769610039\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328840/extras/b24f2f48ff8dd32c72b6bc63f0fdc0bd.webm?t=1769610039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328840/extras/b24f2f48ff8dd32c72b6bc63f0fdc0bd.mp4?t=1769610039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在单人模式中与 AI 对战，或在多人模式中挑战其他玩家。在每场战斗后自由切换指挥官、单位、技能与神器，寻找最适合你的战斗方式——组合无限，乐趣无穷！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >电影式战役</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328840/extras/062eed9e2703cf4c0dcc0b9dd7addd63.poster.avif?t=1769610039\" width=1170 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328840/extras/062eed9e2703cf4c0dcc0b9dd7addd63.webm?t=1769610039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328840/extras/062eed9e2703cf4c0dcc0b9dd7addd63.mp4?t=1769610039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸于充满角色魅力的剧情中，对抗永恒的力量，夺回被 Timefront 吞噬的土地。这款 Roguelite 战役保证每次游玩都带来全新体验与重玩价值。[\\/p]<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自定义游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328840/extras/668742e0e3c0a5ad31559565ba1f8c9e.poster.avif?t=1769610039\" width=1170 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328840/extras/668742e0e3c0a5ad31559565ba1f8c9e.webm?t=1769610039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328840/extras/668742e0e3c0a5ad31559565ba1f8c9e.mp4?t=1769610039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用 Timefront 的游戏编辑器 Worldshaper 创建并发布你自己的游戏模式。如果你的作品在社区中广受欢迎，我们将为你提供推广支持！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[\\/p]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >立即将 Timefront 加入愿望单，加入我们的社区！</p></p></p></p></p></li></ul>",
